protomolt-protobuf-validation-conformance
======================================================

This module vendors the protovalidate conformance harness schema:

  src/main/proto/buf/validate/conformance/harness/harness.proto

Vendored verbatim from the bufbuild/protovalidate project:

  Source:  https://github.com/bufbuild/protovalidate
  Version: v1.2.2
  Commit:  4baed765070e580226a0a30bf2a357cc027dc1f7
  License: Apache License 2.0 (see LICENSE-protovalidate)
  Copyright 2023-2026 Buf Technologies, Inc.

The field-path parsing in FieldPaths.java is a Java port of the
`internal/fieldpath` algorithm from the same project and version, so that
structured FieldPath output matches the conformance runner byte-for-byte.

The vendored file is never modified; the conformance protocol and the
field-path grammar are defined by the upstream project. All other code in
this module is original to protomolt and licensed under the
repository's MIT license.
